# Vicariustab — IT-инвентаризация

Версия: **2.0.12** (`package.json`, `src/config/appConfig.ts`)

## Архитектура

```
├── server.ts                 # Express: API, static, SPA fallback
├── server/
│   ├── dataStore.ts          # JSON/SQL + revision
│   ├── purgeWorkspace.ts     # POST /api/data/purge-workspace
│   ├── userCredentials.ts    # setup, users, seed
│   ├── sessionEngine.ts      # sessions, audit
│   ├── updateEngine.ts       # GitHub update
│   └── workspaceSeed.json    # demo seed on first setup
├── src/
│   ├── App.tsx               # State, CRUD, equipment lifecycle
│   ├── emptyWorkspace.ts     # purge client helpers
│   ├── types.ts
│   ├── components/           # Views + модалки
│   └── utils/                # license, equipment, sync, i18n
└── docker-compose*.yml
```

## Persistence

1. Клиент: `localStorage` (`it_*`) + POST `/api/data` (revision header)
2. `workspaceSync.ts` — persist + `purgeWorkspaceOnServer`
3. Сервер: `dataStore.ts` — encrypted `db.json` или SQL

## Роли

Viewer (read) · Editor (CRUD) · Admin (backup, purge, users, update)

## Разделы UI (`activeTab`)

| Tab | Компонент |
|-----|-----------|
| dashboard | DashboardView |
| objects | ObjectsView |
| computers / peripherals / orgtech / surveillance / consumables / other_equip | ComputersView |
| network | NetworkView |
| employees | EmployeesView |
| warehouse | WarehouseView |
| software | SoftwareView |
| inventory | AuditsView |
| settings | SettingsView (+ backup, purge, update) |

## Утилиты оборудования

| Файл | Назначение |
|------|------------|
| equipmentFields.ts | `inventoryNumbersMatch`, `allocateBatchInventoryNumbers`, `exactInventoryNumberTaken` |
| equipmentDelete.ts | каскадное удаление, preview, software links, `findLinkedStockComputerIds` |
| warehouseRouting.ts | склад→группа, фильтры view, `isStockRegistryDuplicateOfWarehouseBatch` |

## Unified list склада (WarehouseView)

- `whUnified` — позиции warehouseItems
- `stockCompsUnified` — computers «На складе» **только orphans** (без дубля whUnified)
- `compsUnified` / `netUnified` / `softUnified` — выданное оборудование

